The paper discusses common myths in machine learning research, which are relevant to several sub-fields of computer science. However, given the focus on machine learning, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Other relevant categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
